data.description: Discover the epitome of Southern living in this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in the charming community of Lizella. Revel in the timeless appeal of hardwood floors that grace the interior, adding a touch of sophistication to every room. The kitchen boasts newer appliances, making it a stylish and functional space for culinary enthusiasts to create and entertain. Unwind by the fireplace in the living room, creating a cozy ambiance that invites relaxation and warmth. Bask in the natural light of the Florida Room, a perfect spot to enjoy the beauty of every season, creating a seamless connection between indoor and outdoor living. Enjoy the luxury of spacious bedrooms, providing room for personal retreats and comfortable living for everyone in the household. Embrace the convenience of nearby shopping and restaurants, making errands and dining out a breeze for you and your family. Experience the best of both worlds with downtown Macon just a short 20-minute drive away, offering cultural events, entertainment, and a vibrant city life. Enjoy the tranquility of Lizella while still having easy access to the bustling energy of downtown Macon—truly the best of both worlds! Make your move to Lizella – where comfort and convenience meet in this delightful residence!  HVAC: less than 2 years old
